{"name":"help","version":1,"dateBasis":1577024530915,"documents":[{"moodoVer":7,"doc":{"id":"demo-help","version":1,"root":"-LyYDnwKZojggHoK7BG6","text":"Demo","dateModified":1578995368442},"items":[{"id":"-LyYDnwKZojggHoK7BG6","t":"Root","c":1578991566724,"d":1578991566724,"q":true,"o":"demo-help","g":0},{"id":"-LyYDpP4LMOI3sba3yv5","i":"0","t":"# Welcome to Legend","c":1578991572723,"d":1578991580422,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYDnwKZojggHoK7BG6","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYDpP5FldMCsyvSj2P","i":"0","t":"Legend is a flexible and customizable tool that allows you to organize however you like.","c":1578991572724,"d":1578991793756,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYDpP4LMOI3sba3yv5","g":0},{"id":"-LyYEhqYmFlsCe1j4jdr","i":"0,0","t":"This document describes the major features and how you can use them.","c":1578991803921,"d":1578991850055,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYDpP4LMOI3sba3yv5","g":0},{"id":"-LyYEtCY0QRpRiayU3Hf","i":"0,1","t":"","c":1578991850449,"d":1578991850372,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYDpP4LMOI3sba3yv5","g":0},{"id":"-LyYGBwlooEv7xx6nFgy","i":"0,0,0","t":"# Finding Help","c":1578992193439,"d":1578994059029,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYDnwKZojggHoK7BG6","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYGD9yCwuhXGi7eXFA","i":"0","t":"Press / at the beginning of an item to see what all you can do with it. Try it below:","c":1578992198444,"d":1578992209340,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYGBwlooEv7xx6nFgy","g":0},{"id":"-LyYGFux_ihMx-Yogwrd","i":"1","t":"","c":1578992209707,"d":1578992209632,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYGBwlooEv7xx6nFgy","g":0},{"id":"-LyYGMtxtFEQdiTzxJb9","i":"1,0","t":"The intro in the bottom right has lots of helpful hints, and you can bring it up again by clicking the gear icon in the top right and selecting Help.","c":1578992238315,"d":1578993127587,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYGBwlooEv7xx6nFgy","g":0},{"id":"-LyYGTZPRXzP78wxX21j","i":"1,1","t":"See Hotkeys in the gear menu for all the available hotkeys.","c":1578992265608,"d":1578992285355,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYGBwlooEv7xx6nFgy","g":0},{"id":"-LyYHgi8DVb7o_cHydFQ","i":"1,2","t":"","c":1578992585719,"d":1578992589705,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYGBwlooEv7xx6nFgy","g":0},{"id":"-LyYFXKY3oKj_gPqOHH3","i":"0,0,0,0","t":"# The basic structure","c":1578992018897,"d":1578993042910,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYDnwKZojggHoK7BG6","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYHt6jF9Abz4xnbIQ0","i":"-1","t":"**Documents:** You can use multiple documents to separate distinct areas. Click the hamburger icon at the top left to see the documents list. Each document can be shared and (optionally) encrypted.","c":1578992636509,"d":1578993015468,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYFXKY3oKj_gPqOHH3","g":8},{"id":"-LyYIGIuf2d-HWK3-LbT","i":"-1,0","t":"**Panes: **Each pane can give you different views on your data. Panes can open any document, and can be zoomed to focus on a particular item or searched and filtered to customize their view.","c":1578992735592,"d":1578993029161,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYFXKY3oKj_gPqOHH3","g":8},{"id":"-LyYIv4viNFQQ0tePXE9","i":"-1,1","t":"**Boards: **Boards are a collection of panes. You can use multiple boards to easily switch between your workflows.","c":1578992906729,"d":1578992948893,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYFXKY3oKj_gPqOHH3","g":8},{"id":"-LyYDpP5FldMCsyvSj2Q","i":"0","t":"","c":1578991572724,"d":1578992580758,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYFXKY3oKj_gPqOHH3","g":0},{"id":"-LyYEtUTzXSIbO-ZjA3Y","i":"0,0,1","t":"# Outline","c":1578991851596,"d":1578993035261,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYDnwKZojggHoK7BG6","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYEuJGXIM7ykc7anwK","i":"-1","t":"The most basic way to organize in Legend is with hierarchy in the Outline.","c":1578991854975,"d":1578991889421,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYEtUTzXSIbO-ZjA3Y","g":0},{"id":"-LyYF2V0BN9RD9UCJnl6","i":"0","t":"Press Tab and Shift + Tab to indent / outdent in the Outline.","c":1578991892591,"d":1578991919417,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYEuJGXIM7ykc7anwK","g":0},{"id":"-LyYFBTVXOJCHURH-C_E","i":"1","t":"You can expand or collapse Outline items with children by pressing the ∨ icon to the left of them.","c":1578991929358,"d":1578991983722,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYEuJGXIM7ykc7anwK","g":0},{"id":"-LyYFW1va4Uv8inydO3I","i":"2","t":"","c":1578992013609,"d":1578992013551,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYEuJGXIM7ykc7anwK","g":0},{"id":"-LyYFWPRzdVfzwvKhYqf","i":"0,3","t":"# Prefixes","c":1578992015114,"d":1578992634892,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYDnwKZojggHoK7BG6","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYFX9LuqW-YdaUCRCq","i":"-1","t":"You can use prefixes to customize items' display and add features.","c":1578992018180,"d":1578992440513,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYFWPRzdVfzwvKhYqf","g":0},{"id":"-LyYG4wEtTigwkvdy5CD","i":"-1,0","t":"# Projects: Start with # + Space to create a project. Projects are easily zoomable by clicking the ❖ icon.","c":1578992164733,"d":1578993871125,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYFWPRzdVfzwvKhYqf","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYGZVOUuX1GExKEVhv","i":"0","t":"- **Bullets:** Start with - to create a bulleted item. Click the bullet to zoom in.","c":1578992289927,"d":1578993099673,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYG4wEtTigwkvdy5CD","g":1032},{"id":"-LyYGzm2kFef9QexuHT2","i":"2","t":"[ **Tasks: **Start with [ to create a task. Click the checkbox to complete it.","c":1578992401649,"d":1578993106033,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYG4wEtTigwkvdy5CD","g":1032},{"id":"-LyYGwsH2zoqzmWp_pau","i":"3","t":"1. **Numbered Lists:** Start with 1. to create a numbered list.","c":1578992389760,"d":1578993112029,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYG4wEtTigwkvdy5CD","g":1032},{"id":"-LyYH35rd9f0fVJYTnW7","i":"0","t":"Now you can use the search filters (click the search box up top) to filter for projects and tasks.","c":1578992419364,"d":1578992534648,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYFWPRzdVfzwvKhYqf","g":0},{"id":"-LyYJtPAfsGJhVHzSX03","i":"0,0","t":"","c":1578993161968,"d":1578993161899,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYFWPRzdVfzwvKhYqf","g":0},{"id":"-LyYJtVZjmfXPqiWteCT","i":"0,4","t":"# Formatting","c":1578993162386,"d":1578993235280,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYDnwKZojggHoK7BG6","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYKAONLafZ8ARWt_v7","i":"-1","t":"Legend supports rich the standard formatting like **bold, ***italic*, and __underline__.","c":1578993235654,"d":1578993341520,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYJtVZjmfXPqiWteCT","g":8},{"id":"-LyYK_O_d3uU_53stZ6J","i":"-1,0","t":"Highlight some text to see the formatting toolbar for easy access to formatting options.","c":1578993342163,"d":1578993360043,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYJtVZjmfXPqiWteCT","g":0},{"id":"-LyYKB_cPGs5BYmBu_Um","i":"0","t":"","c":1578993240534,"d":1578993240466,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYJtVZjmfXPqiWteCT","g":0},{"id":"-LyYKAVY1K8kDQRmilNJ","i":"0,5","t":"# Dates","c":1578993236113,"d":1578993239174,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYDnwKZojggHoK7BG6","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYHVKbfF8eg6uT1AwK","i":"0","t":"Press ! to open the date picker, where you can select a date/time or type a date yourself.","c":1578992534989,"d":1578993427582,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKAVY1K8kDQRmilNJ","g":0},{"id":"-LyYKuKV5CLJcoFsXaeM","i":"0,0","t":"Legend supports all sorts of repeat dates and durations. See examples of valid repeat dates below:","c":1578993427918,"d":1578994149477,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKAVY1K8kDQRmilNJ","g":0},{"id":"-LyYL4tnJa7ZHlclV-Vn","i":"0,1","t":"Every Monday ﻾ ","b":"f:2;w:0;d:15794784","c":1578993475297,"d":1578993499757,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKAVY1K8kDQRmilNJ","g":4},{"id":"-LyYL7KQExfrudJZhsH7","i":"0,2","t":"Every Tuesday and Friday ﻾ ","b":"f:2;w:1,4;d:15789600","c":1578993485257,"d":1578993498367,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKAVY1K8kDQRmilNJ","g":4},{"id":"-LyYLF9QGVOAZL6oFgVb","i":"0,3","t":"Every 3 days ﻾ ","b":"i:3;f:3;d:15789600","c":1578993517321,"d":1578993542876,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKAVY1K8kDQRmilNJ","g":4},{"id":"-LyYLLboCMLFtDaIDOzj","i":"0,4","t":"Every Tuesday from tomorrow ﻾ ","b":"f:2;w:1;d:15795648","c":1578993543778,"d":1578993557476,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKAVY1K8kDQRmilNJ","g":4},{"id":"-LyYLPP_-xR7bOpAdeyb","i":"0,5","t":"Every Friday until December 21 ﻾ ","b":"f:2;w:4;u:16087057;d:15792192","c":1578993559315,"d":1578993616120,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKAVY1K8kDQRmilNJ","g":4},{"id":"-LyYLSe_NE6ssHhX462v","i":"0,6","t":"Every 14th ﻾ ","b":"f:1;t:14;d:15789600","c":1578993572627,"d":1578993579945,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKAVY1K8kDQRmilNJ","g":4},{"id":"-LyYLUji6og1TT29CGBk","i":"0,7","t":"Every last Friday ﻾ ","b":"f:1;w:4;d:15804288","c":1578993581148,"d":1578993613628,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKAVY1K8kDQRmilNJ","g":4},{"id":"-LyYLZHLd4suJb0h6ld9","i":"0,8","t":"Every other Friday ﻾ ","b":"i:2;f:2;w:4;d:15792192","c":1578993599748,"d":1578993611169,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKAVY1K8kDQRmilNJ","g":4},{"id":"-LyYLcpML0UqkiJUadYD","i":"0,9","t":"Every day from Wednesday until Saturday﻾ ","b":"f:3;d:15790464;u:15793056","c":1578993618373,"d":1578993639952,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKAVY1K8kDQRmilNJ","g":4},{"id":"-LyYLjVXcRB60e5WN8vW","i":"0,10","t":"","c":1578993645712,"d":1578993645648,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKAVY1K8kDQRmilNJ","g":0},{"id":"-LyYQEFo2dToQ82-uRPT","i":"0,5,0","t":"# Tags","c":1578994824396,"d":1578994827273,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYDnwKZojggHoK7BG6","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYQF3N2RzUji6MsSdX","i":"0","t":"","c":1578994827696,"d":1578994827589,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYQEFo2dToQ82-uRPT","g":0},{"id":"-LyYKtiGP3SW8rY5kNzU","i":"0,6","t":"# Views and Sorts","c":1578993425407,"d":1578994036397,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYDnwKZojggHoK7BG6","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYOkMj6lmg8l8v7ZjF","i":"-1","t":"Click the Outline button at the top of this pane to change the view. You can view each pane as:","c":1578994435709,"d":1578994467266,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKtiGP3SW8rY5kNzU","g":0},{"id":"-LyYOsc-bBElyoVBChc2","i":"-1,0","t":"1. **Outline:** The easiest view for quickly entering data with whatever hierarchy you like. ","c":1578994469528,"d":1578994529174,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKtiGP3SW8rY5kNzU","g":1032},{"id":"-LyYP6cJmlIRJeQglQSa","i":"-1,1","t":"1. **List:** A flat list which ignores all hierarchy. This is often most useful combined with search to focus on a specific set of tasks without seeing all the hiearchy around them.","c":1578994530988,"d":1578994620519,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKtiGP3SW8rY5kNzU","g":1032},{"id":"-LyYPHhciVAtftcKWdpM","i":"-1,2","t":"1. **Calendar:** View dated items on a daily, weekly, or monthly calendar view.","c":1578994576384,"d":1578994617420,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKtiGP3SW8rY5kNzU","g":1032},{"id":"-LyYRJR1ffnV5A5T9xXs","i":"-1,3","t":"","c":1578995107728,"d":1578995108383,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKtiGP3SW8rY5kNzU","g":0},{"id":"-LyYPT-x4cJDrQ9om-lf","i":"0","t":"# **Grouping: **","c":1578994622677,"d":1578995149989,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKtiGP3SW8rY5kNzU","g":1032},{"id":"-LyYRTm6pIncFuYWMR5t","i":"0","t":"The Outline and List views also support tons of grouping options to rearrange your view by secondary characters:","c":1578995150111,"d":1578995151334,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYPT-x4cJDrQ9om-lf","g":0},{"id":"-LyYPc2ldoJywkM8HJtr","i":"1","t":"- **Project: **This is a great view for managing by project and hiding items not in projects.","c":1578994663817,"d":1578995156862,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYPT-x4cJDrQ9om-lf","g":1032},{"id":"-LyYPfBQLqE3niJWiZJv","i":"2","t":"- **Tag:** Manage your tasks and projects by tag.","c":1578994676658,"d":1578995156864,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYPT-x4cJDrQ9om-lf","g":1032},{"id":"-LyYPfL41RdfPe-iYM8l","i":"3","t":"- **Contact:** Group tasks together by the person they're attached to.","c":1578994677277,"d":1578995156866,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYPT-x4cJDrQ9om-lf","g":1032},{"id":"-LyYPgi8QaDGQJQHkOMf","i":"4","t":"- **Priority:** Group by high, medium, and low priority, and hide unimportant items.","c":1578994682913,"d":1578995156867,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYPT-x4cJDrQ9om-lf","g":1032},{"id":"-LyYPh-Nqa1Y3OmQM6By","i":"5","t":"- **Agenda:** A special view which includes priority, starred, and dated items. See the **Agenda** section of the settings to customize this view.","c":1578994684079,"d":1578995156869,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYPT-x4cJDrQ9om-lf","g":1032},{"id":"-LyYPjHS6RliELr0RX1y","i":"6","t":"- **Date:** Group items by due date.","c":1578994693429,"d":1578995156870,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYPT-x4cJDrQ9om-lf","g":1032},{"id":"-LyYPjSxHcbSzwCxx8q9","i":"7","t":"- **Created:** Group items by when they were created.","c":1578994694165,"d":1578995156872,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYPT-x4cJDrQ9om-lf","g":1032},{"id":"-LyYPjfcvG_me4g9trPk","i":"8","t":"- **Modified:** Group items by when they were last modified.","c":1578994695040,"d":1578995156873,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYPT-x4cJDrQ9om-lf","g":1032},{"id":"-LyYPjum5LvwTGZxRoLs","i":"9","t":"- **Completed:** Group items by the date you completed them.","c":1578994696010,"d":1578995156874,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYPT-x4cJDrQ9om-lf","g":1032},{"id":"-LyYRWHnf4tew3WbnMhT","i":"0,0","t":"# Sorting:","c":1578995160395,"d":1578995163481,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKtiGP3SW8rY5kNzU","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYRX9-uAJsQtgTW7bJ","i":"0","t":"When you're view items in a grouping, you can sort the groups or items in the groups any way you like:","c":1578995163928,"d":1578995368442,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYRWHnf4tew3WbnMhT","g":0},{"id":"-LyYSAQlZTsWLTii7i2g","i":"1","t":"- Alphabetically","c":1578995333001,"d":1578995339154,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYRWHnf4tew3WbnMhT","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYSC222RacjzKDd743","i":"2","t":"- Number of Items","c":1578995339611,"d":1578995345643,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYRWHnf4tew3WbnMhT","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYSDjfVgojdvTxPBNO","i":"3","t":"- Date","c":1578995346563,"d":1578995347420,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYRWHnf4tew3WbnMhT","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYSEDGMugHuFnlJTxU","i":"4","t":"- Priority","c":1578995348521,"d":1578995349785,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYRWHnf4tew3WbnMhT","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYSEdHzN3-c_Hod4Dx","i":"5","t":"- Date Created","c":1578995350250,"d":1578995353652,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYRWHnf4tew3WbnMhT","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYSFjbwfpTqKhJx3W2","i":"6","t":"- Date Modified","c":1578995354751,"d":1578995356514,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYRWHnf4tew3WbnMhT","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYSGFK6pumw07maLll","i":"7","t":"- Date Completed","c":1578995356844,"d":1578995358934,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYRWHnf4tew3WbnMhT","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYLxd8whN1H5jDlcz1","i":"1","t":"","c":1578993703607,"d":1578994624425,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKtiGP3SW8rY5kNzU","g":0},{"id":"-LyYLnvTRcBJkiPlzwUx","i":"0,8","t":"# Search and Filter","c":1578993663820,"d":1578994204590,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYDnwKZojggHoK7BG6","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYNs0D9zgZCStTZa7G","i":"-1","t":"Click on the search box to see the filters and hints for all of the search features.","c":1578994204852,"d":1578994262769,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYLnvTRcBJkiPlzwUx","g":0},{"id":"-LyYO5FD0FpPjis8EhI0","i":"-1,0","t":"Click each filter to show only matching items, or Cmd/Ctrl click to hide matching items.","c":1578994263164,"d":1578994303145,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYLnvTRcBJkiPlzwUx","g":0},{"id":"-LyYOF4z5fcwPpzGBXVd","i":"-1,1","t":"You can use search and filtering to show or hide certain item types, tags, or contacts. You can enter a date range to restrict results to certain dates. And you can even quickly zoom to any item in the current document.","c":1578994303469,"d":1578994414829,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYLnvTRcBJkiPlzwUx","g":0},{"id":"-LyYLo_yS9gnEuLqaPJJ","i":"0","t":"","c":1578993666540,"d":1578993838605,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYLnvTRcBJkiPlzwUx","g":0},{"id":"-LyYKOJiiP4pOVq_kuUy","i":"0,9","t":"# Notes","c":1578993292700,"d":1578994035745,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYDnwKZojggHoK7BG6","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYN4d0Ypt3OK9iICmR","i":"-1","t":"Press Shift + Enter to add notes to an item. This can be used to add lots of extra information without cluttering your document.","c":1578993998511,"d":1578994019971,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKOJiiP4pOVq_kuUy","g":0},{"id":"-LyYKOs9CVzoJ4mnyf0n","i":"0","t":"","c":1578993294968,"d":1578993294905,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKOJiiP4pOVq_kuUy","g":0},{"id":"-LyYKhaqtRrIzQp4d4He","i":"1","t":"# Interlinking","c":1578993375780,"d":1578994035584,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYDnwKZojggHoK7BG6","g":1024},{"id":"-LyYKjGuCXfkDUFEGF3Q","i":"0","t":"Type [[ to link to other items. Clicking on a linked item will open a popup pane scrolled to the linked item.","c":1578993382632,"d":1578993963496,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKhaqtRrIzQp4d4He","g":0},{"id":"-LyYMxC0du2T0QiYXw5R","i":"1","t":"As an example, a link to Dates: [[-LyYKAVY1K8kDQRmilNJ]]","c":1578993963951,"d":1578993986108,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKhaqtRrIzQp4d4He","g":256},{"id":"-LyYN1vUWma1W60OxDvP","i":"2","t":"","c":1578993987405,"d":1578993987327,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYKhaqtRrIzQp4d4He","g":0},{"id":"-LyYNuq4ZhVrRgUjmjJS","i":"2","t":"# Plugins","c":1578994216435,"d":1578994223014,"o":"demo-help","p":"-LyYDnwKZojggHoK7BG6","g":1024}]}],"boards":{"Tasks":{"id":"Tasks","name":"Tasks","panes":[{"id":"1P1576988199866","item":"-Lvmgm8PXLFPJmFCuDKr","type":"PaneTask","document":"demo-help"}]},"Today":{"id":"Today","name":"Today","panes":[{"id":"2P1576988199866","document":"demo-help","item":"-Lvmgm8PXLFPJmFCuDKr","type":"PaneTask"}]},"Calendar":{"id":"Calendar","name":"Calendar","panes":[{"id":"3P1576988199866","document":"demo-help","item":"-Lvmgm8PXLFPJmFCuDKr","type":"PaneTask","viewState":{"viewMode":"Calendar_Week"}}]}}}